def initialize(module_path)
  super
  pythonpath = ENV['PYTHONPATH'] || ''
  self.env = self.env.merge({ 'PYTHONPATH' => pythonpath + File::PATH_SEPARATOR + File.expand_path('../python', __FILE__) })
end
